{"data":[{"name":"87:1","price":"1. Glorifica el nombre de tu Señor, el Altísimo,","arabic":"سَبِّحِ ٱسۡمَ رَبِّكَ ٱلۡأَعۡلَى","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5949,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es"},{"name":"87:2","price":"2. Quien ha creado todo con perfección y armonía,","arabic":"ٱلَّذِي خَلَقَ فَسَوَّىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5950,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es"},{"name":"87:3","price":"3. ha determinado (el sustento o modo de vida de toda criatura) y las ha guiado (hacia ello),","arabic":"وَٱلَّذِي قَدَّرَ فَهَدَىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5951,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es"},{"name":"87:4","price":"4. y hace brotar el pasto","arabic":"وَٱلَّذِيٓ أَخۡرَجَ ٱلۡمَرۡعَىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5952,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es"},{"name":"87:5","price":"5. que convierte después (tras secarse) en heno oscuro.","arabic":"فَجَعَلَهُۥ غُثَآءً أَحۡوَىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5953,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es"},{"name":"87:6","price":"6. Nos te enseñaremos (el Corán, ¡oh, Muhammad!) y haremos que no lo olvides,","arabic":"سَنُقۡرِئُكَ فَلَا تَنسَىٰٓ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5954,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es"},{"name":"87:7","price":"7. excepto lo que queramos[1137]. En verdad, (tu Señor) conoce todo lo manifiesto y lo oculto.","arabic":"إِلَّا مَا شَآءَ ٱللَّهُۚ إِنَّهُۥ يَعۡلَمُ ٱلۡجَهۡرَ وَمَا يَخۡفَىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5955,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[1137]  Se refiere a cualquier precepto que Al-lah quiera revocar o cambiar por otro.","lang":"es"},{"name":"87:8","price":"8. Y facilitaremos para ti todos tus asuntos (y los preceptos de la religión).","arabic":"وَنُيَسِّرُكَ لِلۡيُسۡرَىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5956,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es"},{"name":"87:9","price":"9. Exhorta, pues, (a los hombres) por si les es de beneficio.","arabic":"فَذَكِّرۡ إِن نَّفَعَتِ ٱلذِّكۡرَىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5957,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es"},{"name":"87:10","price":"10. Quienes teman (a Al-lah) reflexionarán (sobre la exhortación y la aceptarán);","arabic":"سَيَذَّكَّرُ مَن يَخۡشَىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5958,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es"},{"name":"87:11","price":"11. y la despreciarán los desdichados ","arabic":"وَيَتَجَنَّبُهَا ٱلۡأَشۡقَى","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5959,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es"},{"name":"87:12","price":"12. que entrarán en el gran fuego,","arabic":"ٱلَّذِي يَصۡلَى ٱلنَّارَ ٱلۡكُبۡرَىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5960,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es"},{"name":"87:13","price":"13. donde ni moriránni vivirán.","arabic":"ثُمَّ لَا يَمُوتُ فِيهَا وَلَا يَحۡيَىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5961,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es"},{"name":"87:14","price":"14. En verdad, triunfarán quienes se purifiquen (de la incredulidad),","arabic":"قَدۡ أَفۡلَحَ مَن تَزَكَّىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5962,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es"},{"name":"87:15","price":"15. glorifiquen el nombre de su Señor y realicen el salat.","arabic":"وَذَكَرَ ٱسۡمَ رَبِّهِۦ فَصَلَّىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5963,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es"},{"name":"87:16","price":"16. No obstante (¡oh, hombres!), preferís la vida terrenal,","arabic":"بَلۡ تُؤۡثِرُونَ ٱلۡحَيَوٰةَ ٱلدُّنۡيَا","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5964,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es"},{"name":"87:17","price":"17. a pesar de que la otra vida (en el paraíso) es mejor y más duradera.","arabic":"وَٱلۡأٓخِرَةُ خَيۡرٞ وَأَبۡقَىٰٓ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5965,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es"},{"name":"87:18","price":"18. Ciertamente, esto (que ha sido mencionado) aparecía en las primeras revelaciones,","arabic":"إِنَّ هَٰذَا لَفِي ٱلصُّحُفِ ٱلۡأُولَىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5966,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es"},{"name":"87:19","price":"19. en las que recibieron Abraham y Moisés.","arabic":"صُحُفِ إِبۡرَٰهِيمَ وَمُوسَىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5967,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es"}],"chapter":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la","Chapter Al-A'la","A'la","Surah A'la","Chapter A'la","Al A'la","Surah Al A'la","Chapter Al A'la","Surah 87","Chapter 87","The Most High","الأعلى"]}